# ==========================================
# Experiment artefacts that are too heavy for a repo
# ==========================================
# The ``results/robustness/Noise_<pct>pct/mlp_model.pkl`` files total ~several MB.
# Uncomment to drop them from the repo and recompute with ``python -m src.exp_robustness``.
